among broader market barometers, the new york stock exchange's composite index measuring all listed issues rose 0.88 to 151.41. the american stock exchange's market value index rose 1.56 to 295.70
wall street analysts said the market's strength was a good sign that partly reflected a move by investment managers to put unused money to work before the end of the first quarter march 31
the one thing insitutions want to avoid is lack of performance at end of a quarter,'' said philip c. puccio, manager of institutional trading at dillon read &amp; co. in new york
gaining issues outnumbered losers by more than 2-to-1 on the nyse, with 999 up, 427 down and 428 unchanged. volume on the big board totaled 139.26 million shares in the morning session, sharply higher than the 74.69 million traded monday morning
