several oil stocks also rose on takeover speculation, based on the theory that mobil expects $1.2 billion from the sale of its montgomery ward retailing unit and pennzoil will soon get $3 billion from its settlement with texaco. mobil and pennzoil conceivably could use the money for acquisitions
